Package: com.zeshan.phoneaura
Name: PhoneAura
Version: 0.4.2
Architecture: iphoneos-arm64e
Description: Stability rebuild for RootHide iOS 16. Fixes the blank Settings configuration page, removes recursive layout hooks and mixed tab controllers, uses one isolated full-screen overlay for Favorites, Recents, Contacts and Keypad, serializes Contacts and CallHistory access, and keeps PhoneAura Studio for favorite-contact selection.
Maintainer: Next Solution
Author: Next Solution
Section: Tweaks
Depends: firmware (>= 16.0), mobilesubstrate, preferenceloader
